trans-unit.source: Represents the <xref uid="langword_csharp_WsiProfiles" name="WsiProfiles" href=""></xref> element in the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: 表示<xref uid="langword_csharp_WsiProfiles" name="WsiProfiles" href=""></xref>配置文件中的元素。

trans-unit.source: The WsiProfiles element describes the Web Services Interoperability (WSI) specification to which a Web service declares that it conforms.
trans-unit.target: WsiProfiles 元素描述 Web 服务声明，使其符合所 Web 服务互操作性 (WSI) 规范。

trans-unit.source: Initializes and instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement"></xref> class.

Initializes and instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement"></xref> class, using the specified <xref href="System.Web.Services.WsiProfiles"></xref> enumeration value.
trans-unit.target: 初始化与类的实例<xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement"></xref>类，使用指定<xref href="System.Web.Services.WsiProfiles"></xref>枚举值。

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.WsiProfiles"></xref> object that specifies whether the Web service conforms to the WSI Basic Profile version 1.1.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.WsiProfiles"> </xref>对象，它指定 Web 服务是否符合 WSI 基本配置文件版本 1.1。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets whether the Web service conforms to the WSI Basic Profile version 1.1.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置是否符合 WSI 基本配置文件版本 1.1 的 Web 服务。
